text:
After just recently hinting at the release of his third album Astroworld , Travis Scott has taken to social media to preview a new track, quite possibly from the upcoming 2017 project. No details were disclosed along with the Snapchat post, however, which features the Birds In The Trap Sing McKnight artist jamming out to the high-energy tune.
